Package frc.utils

Contains several utility classes, including functions to help with common operations, constants, and several wrappers around core WPILib classes to extend their functionality.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheapCanPidController
    Small wrapper around CANPIDController to reduce CAN usage and overhead.
    CheapCanSparkMax
    Small wrapper around CANSparkMax to reduce CAN usage and overhead.
    CheapWpiTalonSrx
    Small wrapper around WPI_TalonSRX to reduce CAN usage and overhead.
    Constants  
    DpadHelper  
    DriveHelper
    Helper functions for taking human inputs from the drivers and converting them to outputs to the robot.
    DriveSignal
    Small data structure to simplify the issuing of demands to the drivebase by encapsulating the left and right powers as well as whether or not the brakes should be enabled on the drivebase motors or not.
    PidfConstants  
    ShuffleboardWriter  
    UnitConversions
    Helper functions for converting between units.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Constants.DriverHidOption  
    DpadHelper.LastDpadState
    The last recorded value of the DPAD.
